# Commonplace

## Installation

1. `pip install uv`
2. `uv tool install commonplace`

## Tools

- Importers for AI chat providers
- Pre-commit hooks to keep things tidy
- Interactive tool for curating
  - Move and rename
  - Label
  - Summarize and synthesize
